dct_description_sm: Garnier frères éditeurs, gravé par L. Poulmaire.
Relief shown by shading and contour lines.
Shows the river "la Seine", major parcs, cemeteries, important landmarks, buildings, roads, and local railways (existing and under construction) in red.
At lower right margin: Imp. Dufrénoy, 49 ru du Montparnasse, Paris.
